longBusinessSummary: Sinofert Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the production, import and export, distribution, and retail of fertilizer raw materials and crop nutrition products primarily in Mainland China and Macao Special Administrative Region. The company operates through Basic Fertilizers, Distribution, and Production segments. It engages in sourcing and trading of fertilizers including nitrogen, phosphate, and potash; compound fertilizers; and monocalcium and dicalcium phosphate. In addition, the company provides technological research and development, and services relating to the fertilizer business and products; develops agriculture products; and manufactures and sells feed stuffs. In addition, it explores for and exploits phosphate mine. The company was founded in 1993 and is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. Sinofert Holdings Limited operates as a subsidiary of Sinochem Hong Kong (Group) Company Limited.
